channel.title: Help me with Eclipse? [For a 100 error I received]
channel.description:
I have Eclipse Helios. I am new to this program so I'm not very sure on what to do. My friend said I have to debug my one .java so it can find the error, so when I click "Debug" it comes up with an error saying:
"The section cannot be launched, and there are no previous launches"
Anyone know how to work Eclipse, I'd very much appreciate it!
